The '''Royal Engineers''' of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] were notorious for their aftermarket additions to their [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2 units]], making them some of the most sought after units in the [[Galaxy/Legends|galaxy]]. The [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] was one of their products.

